Title: [ANN][PRE-ITO/ICO] 🚀SPIKING - 🐳1000 Whales In Your Wallet🐳
Body: Update June 6, 2018 Spiking x QUOINE Present the World's First Private Sale Conducted on an Exchange!   We are very excited to launch our Private Sale on QUOINE’s innovative ICO Mission Control Platform from today, 6 June to 6 August 2018.  Spiking brings transparency to the cryptocurrency and stock exchanges through real-time verified information on trades made by the Whales. Spiking is the world’s first such platform — a hybrid of stocks and cryptocurrencies in one app, designed to enable users to make informed trading decisions by tracking the verified trading activities of Whales.    How to Participate in Spiking Private Sale  We know that Private Sales are normally hard to access, but with our partnership with QUOINE ICO Market, we are bringing them straight to you.  1. How is someone eligible to participate in the Private Sale?  Eligibility for participation: 1.1 Minimum USD10,000 equivalent crypto account balance in QRYPTOS to unlock the Private Sale. 1.2 Minimum one contribution is USD10,000 to purchase in Tokens in order to be eligible for the Private Sale bonus.   1.3 Only eligible participant will be able to view the Bonus in ICO Market.  As in the ICO Market, the ICO contributor must also agree to the Terms and Conditions of the Token Issuer prior to purchasing the tokens in the Private Sale.  2. How is the Private Sale account balance calculated?  2.1 The Private Sale account balance is calculated based on the value of cryptocurrency holdings in QRYPTOS.   2.2 Cryptocurrency holdings in QUOINEX are not eligible for Private Sale threshold calculation.   2.3 The currencies that are counted in the threshold calculation:  QASH, ETH, BTC BCH (After 18 June)  However please take note, refer to 1.2 in order to contribute in this Private Sale.   Create an account now on QRYPTOS.com to participate in Spiking Private Sale!

Body: SPIKING OFFICIAL PRE-ITO ANNOUNCEMENT THREAD [ Website | Whitepaper | Announcement Thread |  | Facebook | Medium | Twitter | Telegram ]  Try Spiking (Stock) Apps here: https://spiking.com/download  Since 2016, Spiking has offered a state-of-the-art fintech platform that enables tracking of stock moves of over 11,000 sophisticated investors - Blue Whales, Millionaires and Billionaires in the stock market. Now, building on Spiking’s success in the stock market, the company is expanding its unique Follower-Whale protocol and its AI assistant RoboBull into the world of cryptocurrency, with a vision to empower and educate everyday investors and traders of all levels towards financial freedom with peace of mind. The Spiking platform and its tools will empower users to follow and automatically mirror the verified trading activities of Whales, who are highly successful traders or owners of large crypto holdings with access to information before anyone else.   Whale Hunting Referrals  In the spirit of empowering everyday investors with knowledge and information, Spiking wishes to partner directly with industry players who are moving markets — the Whales themselves! In a departure from traditional norms of having a long list of advisors who will benefit from the “reserve pool”, Spiking is inviting these whales to be partners and front the ICO together with the team, thereby sharing in the future success of the project!  As a special campaign launch, we are rewarding users for referring a whale with 8888 Spike Tokens per successful referral! Visit here: https://t.me/SpikingWhaleBot   Whale Partnership  Spiking is setting aside 500,000,000 Spike Tokens (USD5M in value) in a pool for verified partner whales to split evenly. There must be a minimum of 100 whales in this program by the end of the ICO for it to be valid. (E.g, if there are 200 whales in the program, each whale is entitled to 2.5M Spike tokens).
